Package cmput301w14t13.project.models.content

Class Summary
Comment A subclass of CommentTreeElement that represents all CommentTreeElement's that are Replies to Topics or other Comments Used by CreateSubmisionController to create and edit Comments and by TopicView to display all replies to Topics and other Comments
CommentTreeElement The abstract class for Topic, Comment, and Root.
CommentTreeElementSubmission This class is the same as CommentTreeElement.
Root Subclass of CommentTreeElement, it is used to hold a list of Topics Used by HomeView to bring up a list of all Topics for viewing
Topic This class is for top level comments, a subclass of CommentTreeElement.
